Draw line element
Use the [data-draw-line] attribute to specify which element should trigger the line drawing animation on hover.

Draw line box
The script will look for the [data-draw-line-box] attribute and append (random) one of the  elements defined in the svgVariants javascript variable.

Creating your own lines in Figma
We used Figma’s Pencil tool to draw this set of  lines. Just be sure to start from the left, that’s how the script determines the correct draw direction.

